summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of OnTheGo Travels website. Most functionality works correctly with some CTA button issues identified.

ui_bugs.issue: Start Planning Your Trip and Final CTA buttons are not properly wrapped in anchor tags
ui_bugs.details: These buttons should open Google Form in new tab but are missing proper link wrapper

passed_tests: Homepage loads with all sections (hero, trust signals, destinations, how it works, reviews, final CTA)
Navbar navigation works for all visible links (Home, Destinations, Packages, How to Book, Pricing)
Mobile menu toggle works and shows all navigation links including About and Contact
Destinations page filter buttons work correctly
Destination cards open detail modals successfully
Package cards open detail modals successfully
Navbar CTA button opens Google Form in new tab
Hero section primary CTA opens Google Form in new tab
Footer links and social media links work
Contact page Google Form iframe loads correctly
Destination cards navigate to destinations page when clicked
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix CTA button linking: The 'Start Planning Your Trip' button in How It Works section and 'Final CTA' button in the final section need to be properly wrapped in anchor tags with Google Form URL and target='_blank' attribute
success_percentage: frontend: 90% - Most features work correctly with minor CTA button issues
